50|$|Junior {{firefighting}} is a {{youth activity}} mostly organized by <b>fire</b> <b>departments.</b> It {{serves as a}} means of personal development for the youths, as well as a recruiting pool for the <b>fire</b> <b>departments.</b>|$|R
