50|$|In Finland the {{firefighting}} in {{the countryside}} mostly depends on volunteer <b>fire</b> <b>departments,</b> nearly always with {{a contract with the}} regional emergency authorities (or, formerly and in Åland, the municipality). There are volunteer <b>fire</b> <b>departments</b> also in cities, but there with a minor role.|$|R
